title: The Gavin McInnes Show 2016-09-20
description: Today on TGMS, Gavin wants the parents of the Chelsea bomber to suffer, then watches a dance mob for refugees. Steven Crowder comes on to talk about his Young Turk's parody. Matt Welch gets in studio just before CopperCab, aka ClaireCab, Skypes in from his backyard. After Claire rage quits the interview, Gavin and Matt debate about immigrants and open borders. Lauren Southern then Skypes in to discuss problems with refugees in Europe
